*Predivno* je videti svet u svetlucavim bojama. (It is wonderful to see the world in glimmering colors.) 

Vreme je *predivno* za šetnju. (The weather is lovely for a walk.)

On je *predivno* govorio o ljubavi. (He spoke wonderfully about love.)

Ona se oseća *predivno*. (She feels wonderful.)

*Predivno* je biti obdaren dobrim zdravljem. (It is wonderful to be blessed with good health.)